func:
let word = msg.word;
let payload = msg.payload;
let dia = msg.payload.split(" ")[1]
let mes = msg.payload.split(" ")[0]
if (mes == 'January' && !payload.includes(word)) msg.payload = dia + '/01'
else if (mes == 'February' && !payload.includes(word)) msg.payload = dia + '/02'
else if (mes == 'March' && !payload.includes(word)) msg.payload = dia + '/03'
else if (mes == 'April' && !payload.includes(word)) msg.payload = dia + '/04'
else if (mes == 'May' && !payload.includes(word)) msg.payload = dia + '/05'
else if (mes == 'June' && !payload.includes(word)) msg.payload = dia + '/06'
else if (mes == 'July' && !payload.includes(word)) msg.payload = dia + '/07'
else if (mes == 'August' && !payload.includes(word)) msg.payload = dia + '/08'
else if (mes == 'September' && !payload.includes(word)) msg.payload = dia + '/09'
else if (mes == 'October' && !payload.includes(word)) msg.payload = dia + '/10'
else if (mes == 'November' && !payload.includes(word)) msg.payload = dia + '/11'
else if (mes == 'December' && !payload.includes(word)) msg.payload = dia + '/12'
else msg.payload == "";
return msg;
